y for a plain-text-only local demo endpoint.\n", "message": "Add false-positive waiver for rule 10021 (X-Content-Type-Options missing) on text-only demo", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "zap/baseline.conf", "repo": "T14_R01_C02_A01", "sha": "44d7c5b3c3a345a02f3debec6c52ca6bd2c001ac"}, "id": "call_afa6133cf06f499c8c748763", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"branch": "main", "content": "# Rule Waivers\n\nWaivers must include rule id, action, and local-demo justification.\n\n| Rule ID | Action | Justification |\n|---------|--------|---------------|\n| 10021 | IGNORE | X-Content-Type-Options header is unnecessary for a plain-text-only local demo endpoint; MIME-type sniffing is not a concern when the server serves only `text/plain` content. |\n", "message": "Document false-positive waiver for rule 10021 in rule_waivers.md", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "docs/rule_waivers.md", "repo": "T14_R01_C02_A01", "sha": "f9831b0f02c92113e31a5dfbe9a85e536772658f"}, "id": "call_81d6c32937ce46f3b8e5229b", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 6594, "output_tokens": 1221, "total_tokens": 7815, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 6272}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 622}}}}]}}}
